~ start
Hey do you know Mister Cent?
Bill: Mister Cent? 
They fired him recently.
Bill: Oh yeah, that guy!
They said Pennies don't exist any more.
AND that he only taxed people a cent.
I miss him.
Bill: Maybe you can quit.
OHHHHH YEEAAHHH! Why didn't I think of that.
